  { '@type': 'Question', name: 'What should post-workout gummies contain?', acceptedAnswer: { '@type': 'Answer', text: 'The most evidence-backed post-workout ingredients include: (1) Tart cherry extract — rich in anthocyanins that reduce exercise-induced inflammation and muscle soreness (DOMS). A meta-analysis found tart cherry reduced muscle soreness by 13% and accelerated strength recovery. (2) BCAAs (branched-chain amino acids) — leucine, isoleucine, and valine stimulate muscle protein synthesis and reduce muscle protein breakdown post-exercise. (3) Electrolytes — sodium, potassium, and magnesium replenish minerals lost through sweat. (4) Collagen peptides — provide glycine and proline for connective tissue repair. (5) Turmeric/curcumin — reduces exercise-induced inflammation via COX-2 inhibition. (6) Glutamine — supports gut barrier integrity and immune function post-exercise. The best post-workout gummies combine 2-3 of these ingredients at clinically relevant doses.' } },
