    <p>Nuun is the electrolyte brand trusted by professional endurance athletes, and their recovery gummies apply that hydration expertise to gummy format. The 300mg sodium per serving is the most meaningful electrolyte dose in our evaluation — sodium is the primary mineral lost in sweat (average 500-1,500mg per hour of exercise) and the most critical to replace for rehydration, muscle function, and prevention of hyponatremia. Added potassium and magnesium round out the electrolyte panel for comprehensive mineral replenishment.</p>

